00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem.

435
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] šutkova od Bogu.

436
00:31:04,000 --> 00:31:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od svog njega.

437
00:31:05,000 --> 00:31:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite još ovo.

438
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I žena od jednog dilera od kojeg sam uzimao po krajini.

439
00:31:13,000 --> 00:31:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Njegova žena me dodi u šutkova zajednog svina.

440
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Možete vidjeti kako ta žena moli za svog muža.

441
00:31:21,000 --> 00:31:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Iče žena doživa tamo živoga Boga.

442
00:31:27,000 --> 00:31:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem.

443
00:31:28,000 --> 00:31:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem.

444
00:31:29,000 --> 00:31:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pazi se da ona muž ukrade.

445
00:31:30,000 --> 00:31:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene.

446
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da se ja spasim.

447
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tolazim u šutkova.

448
00:31:34,000 --> 00:31:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gužba.

449
00:31:35,000 --> 00:31:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Lodnica.

450
00:31:36,000 --> 00:31:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam glavo stavio iz ljudi mogu dole.

451
00:31:39,000 --> 00:31:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sramo je bilo.

452
00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo me sramo.

453
00:31:43,000 --> 00:31:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Izlazi frajivo.

454
00:31:46,000 --> 00:31:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni to nište nije bilo uopče interesantno nište.

455
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Frajivo mogu izrači moj tata.

456
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne bi bilo uopče nište.

457
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam vjeroval.

458
00:31:56,000 --> 00:31:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I nisam zavlja što mi se događa.

459
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem naprav frajivo počne.

460
00:32:04,000 --> 00:32:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čunio ovaj govani biće.

461
00:32:06,000 --> 00:32:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pre meni bilo interesantno.

462
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znate gospodin kako će sa mnom.

463
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ovaj.

464
00:32:12,000 --> 00:32:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I krenu svjedočanstva.

465
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja ne držam glavo.

466
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da me niko ne vidi, ne bože.

467
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Učer sam glavnih mi tamo.

468
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja čujem svjedočanstva.

469
00:32:24,000 --> 00:32:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Izlazi neki stari onako čaj.

470
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo iz Bosne.

471
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] On vidi se po glasu da čaj poštem da je sve.

472
00:32:30,000 --> 00:32:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] I on će.

473
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Evo ja ozdravim tu.

474
00:32:34,000 --> 00:32:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Vidite, ono ozdravim je Bog Isusa.

475
00:32:36,000 --> 00:32:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta je očin?

476
00:32:39,000 --> 00:32:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je neka ženska surođena od ovog.

477
00:32:46,000 --> 00:32:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Polako ja dižem i lagu.

478
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo na polaganje ruku.

479
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa to je u mene, to nije bilo strah.

480
00:32:54,000 --> 00:32:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa ne kaže strah.

481
00:32:55,000 --> 00:32:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma kako?

482
00:32:56,000 --> 00:32:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo na polaganje ruku.

483
00:32:58,000 --> 00:33:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazim na polaganje ruku.

484
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:03,000
[UNKNOWN] Bilo bi na kraju gore stepenica.

485
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:04,000
[UNKNOWN] Dolaj isto.

486
00:33:04,000 --> 00:33:05,000
[UNKNOWN] Polaganje ruku.

487
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:07,000
[UNKNOWN] Sumne brošičaje kremu stavili ruku.

488
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam odletio tri metra od uga.

489
00:33:09,000 --> 00:33:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kao boksača kad pogodiš,

490
00:33:11,000 --> 00:33:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] a ne da vam opadnili u ruku.

491
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam ja stao,

492
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja osjetio takvu silu,

493
00:33:18,000 --> 00:33:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] duha svetove,

494
00:33:20,000 --> 00:33:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] jako i iz vlastitog iskustva,

495
00:33:23,000 --> 00:33:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] govorim da sam doživio sve najgore.

496
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I težio biti najgor,

497
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] i bio sam najgor.

498
00:33:29,000 --> 00:33:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam stao,

499
00:33:33,000 --> 00:33:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad sam se ja vratio u Zagrebu.

500
00:33:37,000 --> 00:33:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije mi mogo nikog potlika za glavu,

501
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] na trebu.

502
00:33:41,000 --> 00:33:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa svima.

503
00:33:42,000 --> 00:33:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znate mi šta je ovo,

504
00:33:43,000 --> 00:33:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] znate onaj kran kad padne,

505
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] ono sve da padne na me ne može tako.

506
00:33:46,000 --> 00:33:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam svaku subotu i nedelju s autobusima

507
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] išao u Šurkova.

508
00:33:51,000 --> 00:33:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve što sam tražio u životu,

509
