608
00:36:03,000 --> 00:36:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] onako pisano hrv slovenjano slo,

609
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja mu pričam sa svoje jade,

610
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:10,000
