612
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] no ovako kuka nad me,

613
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] no ovako bože,

614
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:18,000
[SPEAKER_00] ovdje nema štosti.

615
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad,

616
00:36:23,000 --> 00:36:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] dobro je naredan,

617
00:36:24,000 --> 00:36:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] meni mi ovdje sve da hoće tu kući,

618
00:36:26,000 --> 00:36:28,000
