623
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] neće me ono čut,

624
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] neće ovo neće ovo.

625
00:36:36,000 --> 00:36:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad dolazim nekom,

626
00:36:37,000 --> 00:36:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] i dolazim ja nared,

627
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:39,000
