628
00:36:39,000 --> 00:36:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] si sredo što ide tako.

629
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dolazim ti s imenom svećenike,

630
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] jedan mnogo visoki čovjek,

631
00:36:47,000 --> 00:36:48,000
