633
00:36:50,000 --> 00:36:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad sad se ja nagledno vidim kako na ploče sam se promijela,

634
00:36:56,000 --> 00:36:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] piše A. Rebić.

635
00:36:58,000 --> 00:37:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ovo je ljepona češća i nije sam čuo za ovo.

636
00:37:01,000 --> 00:37:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja sam ljudski, sam to je to.

637
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazim ja na red,

638
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] to je pokodnje dolojte Rebića.

639
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] dolazim na red,

640
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] ulazim unutra.

641
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ja gledam na pokazane mrežice,

642
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] dižem na glavo Grdaninja,

643
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja imam:

644
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ko je tam?"

645
00:37:16,000 --> 00:37:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je krenulo moje kaljenje,

646
00:37:20,000 --> 00:37:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] katarza,

647
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] plakanje.

648
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikada nisam vidio do tada,

649
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer sem bio slijep,

650
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] nisam vidio toliko radost,

651
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] da se niko radio zbog mene.

652
00:37:35,000 --> 00:37:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja gledam sve čujka.

653
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] On u onoj radosti počinje meni govoriti.

654
00:37:43,000 --> 00:37:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vratio se razvratni sin.

655
00:37:46,000 --> 00:37:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Otac mu oblači bijele haljine.

656
00:37:51,000 --> 00:37:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da sam se raspao.

657
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] dođelo pameti sve s mene.

658
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bi tako radosti.

659
00:37:58,000 --> 00:38:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vratio se razvratni sin.

660
00:38:02,000 --> 00:38:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog se radoval.

661
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,000
[UNKNOWN] Kad sam se vratio,

662
00:38:05,000 --> 00:38:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] kao za svakoga od nas nije tražio izgovele.

663
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si bio šta sami, pa kako sam, pa ovo sam, pa zašto vam.

664
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] No se radoval.

665
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zagledio me i radovalo se.

666
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od ovom momentu,

667
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] toliko je bio sretan veličastni Adalber,

668
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] da je rekao:

669
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Išlo se i našli sa mnom, meni nije bilo došao."

670
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Sada ti je sad da teare graju odriješeno."

671
00:38:32,000 --> 00:38:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije vadao.

672
00:38:34,000 --> 00:38:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, odriješeno je.

673
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazimo.

674
00:38:39,000 --> 00:38:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tam odim u prve redu.

675
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite da nito je sam.

676
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog me dolašao.

677
00:38:43,000 --> 00:38:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi su pobjegli od mene.

678
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se znam, našli pokli u mene i biskupi, i mafije, i braća, i sestre.

679
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Novalja uča.

680
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije.

681
00:38:55,000 --> 00:39:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Treba se vratiti do Novalja, počinje sezona.

682
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Četvrti mjesec.

683
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vraćam se ja u Novalja.

684
00:39:05,000 --> 00:39:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, u Zagrebu, pardon, izpećam se.

685
00:39:08,000 --> 00:39:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam u Zagrebu,

686
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] meni nešto zove u koju će ići na hodočašću.

687
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja uzmem ruksak, odlazim u Novalju,

688
00:39:17,000 --> 00:39:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] prispavam kod bratovi 13. crkve Sv. Katarine

689
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:22,000
[UNKNOWN] i krenem grijem sam iz Novalja u Međuguru.

690
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:24,000
[UNKNOWN] ovi su uvijek na ovaj.

691
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:25,000
[UNKNOWN] Do sada je bio ludo.

692
00:39:25,000 --> 00:39:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] Novalja u Međuguru je nikakav hodočašćić.

693
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Počinje sezona, treba s novcem, treba zaraditi.

694
00:39:36,000 --> 00:39:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali je i gospodin mi je poslao.

695
00:39:38,000 --> 00:39:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kroz evanđeje.

696
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve ostaje.

697
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:43,000
[UNKNOWN] Sve ostaje.

698
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ostaje.

699
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, ne za mnom.

700
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, odlazim.

701
00:39:48,000 --> 00:39:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Novalja, Međugurje.

702
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Inače, po svim normalnim ovim, po tom hodanju, to treba proći za 8 dana, ja sam 14.

703
00:39:57,000 --> 00:39:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] po tom hodanju.

704
00:39:58,000 --> 00:40:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti god bi došla sretan, ljudi te pozdravljaju.

705
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim, bilo je tu i svojom silom.

706
00:40:04,000 --> 00:40:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja još uvijek nisam znao i prepoznati silu Duha Svetoga.

707
00:40:09,000 --> 00:40:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] ići Duhom Svetim, hodati Duhom Svetim, razločivanje Duhom.

708
00:40:13,000 --> 00:40:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja hodam, prvi dan sam hodao u 40 km, tamo sam jedno veliko saobraćenje na Vesać, u Prometno, u Kodinčke, pod mosta.

709
00:40:22,000 --> 00:40:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tamo sam spao, spavam ja na grovlju, crka, grovlju, ništa.

710
00:40:25,000 --> 00:40:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene, gospodin mi je sad dao takvu hrabrost.

711
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zna mi se što je bilo u tim ljudima u glavi.

712
00:40:30,000 --> 00:40:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni imali u tom lokale, ljudi čekaju, treba raditi u glavi, što ćeš se mu neče.

713
00:40:36,000 --> 00:40:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi dan, na papiru je to bilo ljeko izgledalo, svaki dan 30 km, dođu i tomate.

714
00:40:41,000 --> 00:40:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako je ovo je bilo to već.

715
00:40:43,000 --> 00:40:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] 40 km, oči ja svojom silom.

716
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad se već ja znam, obratit ću se i sad opet ću ja po svome.

717
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem ja u Međugorje, obratim se, vratim se, nazav.

718
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer do tad sam u Međugorje, neka mi Bog oprosti, dolazi ko na otru usni kogogor.

719
00:40:56,000 --> 00:40:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odem na križu, od svog bio sam tamo i dalje ja po svome.

720
00:40:59,000 --> 00:41:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Strašno jadno.

721
00:41:03,000 --> 00:41:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] I padnem tamo kad posljedim, glava ide, noge ne otekle, krva ne ide.

722
00:41:08,000 --> 00:41:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ima otvordoglavost.

723
00:41:10,000 --> 00:41:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ono što ti gospodin dao, pokazao mi je, pokazao mi je, takvu ljubav, kako novo svijet ne postoji.

724
00:41:19,000 --> 00:41:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na neko ne odostaje.

725
00:41:21,000 --> 00:41:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nobuna, oko 10 km per.

726
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] To što sam tamo djeto už ono spomenil u pridrazi.

727
00:41:27,000 --> 00:41:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi me snaju, zači ti sopkih i hmiljeja.

728
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čuli su da je da neki luđak.

729
00:41:32,000 --> 00:41:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Međugorje pješi.

730
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on dođe poznao me čovjek.

731
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Rustičeš ti."

732
00:41:38,000 --> 00:41:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Hajdemo u Međugorje."

733
00:41:40,000 --> 00:41:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] I nekako sam ja došao do Međugorje.

734
00:41:42,000 --> 00:41:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] U međugorje, u međugorje se nastavio.

735
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Plaćam nam cestijalno i ravno i tamo.

736
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ljuboškotno i plaćam.

737
00:41:49,000 --> 00:41:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da življam milost.

738
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, gospod, nisam vidio.

739
00:41:53,000 --> 00:41:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da življam takvu milost.

740
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Takav dodir majke.

741
00:41:57,000 --> 00:42:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Takav zagrijaja majke što sam cijeli život tražio.

742
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moja majka mi to nije mogla dati.

743
00:42:03,000 --> 00:42:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je umirala, zvali su mi sestra i braća.

744
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dođi, a majka umirala je od ranaca.

745
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Raki, oča, rak svega.

746
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam došao.

747
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad znam ko mi je dao tatu.

748
00:42:16,000 --> 00:42:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da sam tamo bio noć prije, ne znam, di.

749
00:42:19,000 --> 00:42:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja dolazim.

750
00:42:21,000 --> 00:42:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ono je bila u Kolmijare.

751
00:42:23,000 --> 00:42:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Šapljim na ukovo.

752
00:42:26,000 --> 00:42:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad viš tamo, da će biti mina.

753
00:42:30,000 --> 00:42:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uprosti mi, joj pa šta ti za sve.

754
00:42:33,000 --> 00:42:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znam se da se minuluje na par sati.

755
00:42:36,000 --> 00:42:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Spasila se.

756
00:42:40,000 --> 00:42:42,000
[UNKNOWN] I ovaj...

757
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vraćam se iz Međuga jer dolazim u Noilju.

758
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi u Noilju gledaju mene.

759
00:42:49,000 --> 00:42:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi.

760
00:42:50,000 --> 00:42:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hrvatska, Brazilia.

761
00:42:52,000 --> 00:42:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni smo je tako bilo to na prvenstvo.

762
00:42:53,000 --> 00:42:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Niko ne gleda utaknicu.

763
00:42:54,000 --> 00:42:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi gledali na tri lokala.

764
00:42:56,000 --> 00:42:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svi gledali mene šta ću ja napraviti.

765
00:42:58,000 --> 00:43:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer sam i osvet, jer sam lud, jer sam ne znam šta.

766
00:43:01,000 --> 00:43:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tad nešto je bilo s Brazilom, nemam pojma i ja skočim.

767
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ono je ovo.

768
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se posvađam sa svima.

769
00:43:12,000 --> 00:43:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znau Bog kak.

770
00:43:13,000 --> 00:43:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se posvađam sa svima.

771
00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve ostavljam, dolazim u Zagrebu.

772
00:43:18,000 --> 00:43:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Još uvijek ne znam kako sam završio s paterikeom u Gunji.

773
00:43:21,000 --> 00:43:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi osmi, špica sezone.

774
00:43:23,000 --> 00:43:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam sve ostavio dole.

775
00:43:25,000 --> 00:43:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Brat je preuzio dobavljači.

776
00:43:27,000 --> 00:43:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su velike cifre novaca bili.

777
00:43:29,000 --> 00:43:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] To su milioni kuna.

778
00:43:31,000 --> 00:43:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Di je ovaj prelučan Bog?

779
00:43:33,000 --> 00:43:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma koji Bog? Treba raditi.

780
00:43:35,000 --> 00:43:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako? Šta? Ljud su uložili na mene.

781
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da li je to pošteno, nepošteno?

782
00:43:39,000 --> 00:43:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne bitno.

783
00:43:40,000 --> 00:43:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije bilo pošteno.

784
00:43:42,000 --> 00:43:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prvi osmi, ja sa Župnikom i onim Ivanom Matićem krvamo tamo kuće.

785
00:43:47,000 --> 00:43:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] To izlaze na nove TV.

786
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni gledaju, ćuš treba.

787
00:43:51,000 --> 00:43:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam živio za to.

788
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Za moć, za te novce, za to.

789
00:43:57,000 --> 00:43:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zrče, tamo sam bio doma.

790
00:43:59,000 --> 00:44:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada nekako...

791
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Suditi?

792
00:44:03,000 --> 00:44:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

793
00:44:04,000 --> 00:44:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bo kaže, ne sudi nikome.

794
00:44:06,000 --> 00:44:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ti ljudi na Zrče su izgubljeni.

795
00:44:09,000 --> 00:44:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja su bolji ljudi bio se izvajem.

796
00:44:11,000 --> 00:44:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Gunji doživljavam nešto totalno drugačije.

797
00:44:17,000 --> 00:44:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bake sredne.

798
00:44:18,000 --> 00:44:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vidim da se da...

799
00:44:19,000 --> 00:44:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bake, da od sredne nosiš im hranu.

800
00:44:22,000 --> 00:44:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi su u toj, znači, tom svemu, u toj nebolji, u toj nesreći.

801
00:44:27,000 --> 00:44:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da živjavaš gospodine?

802
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

803
00:44:30,000 --> 00:44:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazim mrtvini.

804
00:44:31,000 --> 00:44:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim pojmojim za to niječe.

805
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako mrtvini?

806
00:44:34,000 --> 00:44:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja šta?

807
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodine daje mili.

808
00:44:36,000 --> 00:44:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] S tim mladim.

809
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja 17 dana budem.

810
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] 17 dana sam bio tamo.

811
00:44:40,000 --> 00:44:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon dva tjedna.

812
00:44:42,000 --> 00:44:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da svaki tjedan se to mijenja.

813
00:44:44,000 --> 00:44:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon dva tjedna.

814
00:44:45,000 --> 00:44:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Među su tamo svi zavodnje.

815
00:44:48,000 --> 00:44:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne vidim da me izgunje nigdje.

816
00:44:49,000 --> 00:44:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da mi mi kaže: "Patrike, roko ideš doma?"

817
00:44:54,000 --> 00:44:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja?

818
00:44:56,000 --> 00:44:57,000
[UNKNOWN] Imam šans.

819
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam da poslušao.

820
00:44:58,000 --> 00:44:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Stam bolno mi šta je.

821
00:44:59,000 --> 00:45:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nikom nisam bio poslušao.

822
00:45:01,000 --> 00:45:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikom je na žalost.

823
00:45:03,000 --> 00:45:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ideš doma?

824
00:45:05,000 --> 00:45:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako sam pričao sve čini?

825
00:45:09,000 --> 00:45:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako doma?

826
00:45:10,000 --> 00:45:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu svi me vola, radim, super.

827
00:45:11,000 --> 00:45:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mladim.

828
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zovem ja Borisa Milka prijatelja koji je zadnji sličin i ovaj...

829
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pozdali smo sve u ovu torbos iza Šurkovac i...

830
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] I moram biti ja...

831
00:45:25,000 --> 00:45:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] I zovem ja lijeka.

832
00:45:30,000 --> 00:45:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Borisa, ovaj mene tijelo doma.

833
00:45:32,000 --> 00:45:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zovem še biti.

834
00:45:33,000 --> 00:45:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ja doma nema.

835
00:45:34,000 --> 00:45:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ne idem ja on ovo ili nema šanski, znam šta je to dole.

836
00:45:37,000 --> 00:45:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže mi: "Moraš biti poslušan."

837
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Moraš biti poslušan."

838
00:45:43,000 --> 00:45:44,000
[UNKNOWN] "Moraš biti poslušan."

839
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,000
[UNKNOWN] A što, bolesno...

840
00:45:45,000 --> 00:45:49,000
[UNKNOWN] I zove mene baterika sve strane.

841
00:45:49,000 --> 00:45:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže: "Idi, zvaći te za tijena dana."

842
00:45:53,000 --> 00:45:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Ali nema, ali mene ljudi tu!"

843
00:45:55,000 --> 00:45:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] I vidim.

844
00:45:57,000 --> 00:45:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan je bila misla.

845
00:45:58,000 --> 00:46:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, gospodi me ozdravlja.

846
00:46:00,000 --> 00:46:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] U tome, sve tu me ozdravlja.

847
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja odlazim nakon tijena dana, ono me zove nazad.

848
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam mogo spavati.

849
00:46:07,000 --> 00:46:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam čekao samo taj povez.

850
00:46:09,000 --> 00:46:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam.

851
00:46:10,000 --> 00:46:11,000
[UNKNOWN] Ja nisam.

852
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam spomenuo ozdravljenje.

853
00:46:14,000 --> 00:46:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svijeduće vam sada je ozdravljenje svoje.

854
00:46:16,000 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, gospodin me ozdravlja.

855
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ozdravlja me živčani sustav.

856
00:46:19,000 --> 00:46:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imao sam skoro rak želuca.

857
00:46:22,000 --> 00:46:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, kod Kujunčića sam išao doktora pet puta gastroskopije.

858
00:46:25,000 --> 00:46:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije bi bilo više lijeka.

859
00:46:26,000 --> 00:46:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tablete su hraneve, helikobakteri, gastritis.

860
00:46:29,000 --> 00:46:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve to gospodin ozdravlja.

861
00:46:31,000 --> 00:46:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Panič napade na aksioznost.

862
00:46:33,000 --> 00:46:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Strahove.

863
00:46:34,000 --> 00:46:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, potrezu iz mozga, to je ta...

864
00:46:39,000 --> 00:46:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto nekako lapa.

865
00:46:40,000 --> 00:46:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin je ozdravlja i počeo ozdravljati.

866
00:46:44,000 --> 00:46:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Malo pa malo sve.

867
00:46:50,000 --> 00:46:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vraćam se ja sada završena.

868
00:46:52,000 --> 00:46:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Buljno dolazim ja u novaljno.

869
00:46:53,000 --> 00:46:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prije toga, da. Prije toga završeno na kamenitim vratom.

870
00:46:59,000 --> 00:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isto, borili smo dvete na kamenita vrata.

871
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazim tamo, klećim.

872
00:47:02,000 --> 00:47:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hršica me zna iz onog života.

873
00:47:04,000 --> 00:47:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam uvijek me pratio, bio sam kao neka paca.

874
00:47:07,000 --> 00:47:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on je ovako, kada je vidio tamo da ja klećim.

875
00:47:10,000 --> 00:47:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to kaže: "Poznat mi je neko onako sleđa."

876
00:47:13,000 --> 00:47:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se dim, kak prodoglava ove kleći.

877
00:47:16,000 --> 00:47:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Navalio, ne diže se.

878
00:47:18,000 --> 00:47:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže on, kad sem se divil,

879
00:47:20,000 --> 00:47:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] kaže: "Gospodine, kao ćeš mi još iznaditi."

880
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tad sam krenul s njima i s kamenitim vratima,

881
00:47:27,000 --> 00:47:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] i s tom zajednicom.

882
00:47:28,000 --> 00:47:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] I odem dola od novaljom.

883
00:47:32,000 --> 00:47:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemog ja biti tam.

884
00:47:36,000 --> 00:47:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kopam, tražim, želim Krista, želim Isusa, želim tu ljubav.

885
00:47:39,000 --> 00:47:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazim i negdje pročitam ili čujem od svečenika Marije Magdalena

886
00:47:44,000 --> 00:47:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] kako je tražila Isusa, ona je htjela upoznati Isusa.

887
00:47:47,000 --> 00:47:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] I tada, na kraju svog mjeseca,

888
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja mi koja mora niče neko hodno češća.

889
00:47:57,000 --> 00:48:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, već, ja počem to slušati, učiti o duhovima, o sebi, o oholosti, šta, kako, o razlučivanju duhova.

890
00:48:11,000 --> 00:48:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ovaj, kažem ja, šta je sad mala gospa?

891
00:48:15,000 --> 00:48:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Idem ja pješica iz Novavlje preko Trsata, Mariju Visticu, sam.

892
00:48:19,000 --> 00:48:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali idem ja vidjeti da li je to od mene, da li od Boga ili od vraga.

893
00:48:29,000 --> 00:48:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gledam, ne mogu stičiti da će li čunan, ne mogu stičiti na malo gosti.

894
00:48:33,000 --> 00:48:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ma nije to.

895
00:48:35,000 --> 00:48:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, šta je bilo moje.

896
00:48:37,000 --> 00:48:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] U jednom putu na Facebooku izlazim, kako sam rekao na kameniti vratima, da ću u zajednici, ja ću ovdje doći pješice i neko je to lajkao.

897
00:48:47,000 --> 00:48:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] I to je tako meni izašlo u kraju 8 mjeseca na mobitelju.

898
00:48:53,000 --> 00:49:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] I onda vidim status, valjda kaptoval, nevam, pojam, pišem, 30. i 14. zavitov oddačašće grada, zavimo Mariju Visticu.

899
00:49:03,000 --> 00:49:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] I su rekao, to je, ja, ruksak.

900
00:49:05,000 --> 00:49:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nikad neću da volim svoga brata.

901
00:49:07,000 --> 00:49:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, brat, mlađo od mene je šest godina.

902
00:49:10,000 --> 00:49:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio sam mu svet, znači oni su svi upatrali za mene, braća i sestre, jer sam ja bio sposoban, snalažen.

903
00:49:15,000 --> 00:49:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oma je rekla, ma roko, četaj, sve roko može.

904
00:49:18,000 --> 00:49:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su jedno upatrali za mene, osim za Boga.

905
00:49:22,000 --> 00:49:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] I meni brat kaže: "Ako mi sad ostaviš, više nikad ne si imao brata."

906
00:49:28,000 --> 00:49:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] A on ne zna da meni gospodin to spaša, a ja ne mogu nikom to objasniti.

907
00:49:32,000 --> 00:49:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on meni kaja: "Javić, ne, ja jedim za Isusa."

908
00:49:36,000 --> 00:49:38,000
[UNKNOWN] Tiško.

909
00:49:38,000 --> 00:49:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja uzimam ruksak i hodam baš u duhu.

910
00:49:44,000 --> 00:49:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baš mi duhu sveti vodio, ja sam se otvorio, 14 dana hodam.

911
00:49:51,000 --> 00:49:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tovalja, Trsat, Zagreb, Marija Bislica.

912
00:49:55,000 --> 00:49:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sam ću vam još nešto izpričati.

913
00:49:57,000 --> 00:49:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Niti ja nisam htio spavati, samo na cesti.

914
00:49:59,000 --> 00:50:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam htio dozvoliti uopće malo nekog konfora.

915
00:50:03,000 --> 00:50:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Poznavajući sebe kakav sam bio, ko zna ti bi to odišlo.

916
00:50:07,000 --> 00:50:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dozi na kamenita, Krešo Škarić je na prijatelj.

917
00:50:13,000 --> 00:50:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] I zaukoš: "Daj spavaj tu kod mjena." On je gledan tamo.

918
00:50:15,000 --> 00:50:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne ide dok od trga živi.

919
00:50:17,000 --> 00:50:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa daj tu, nema šansi. Ja spavam na kamenita rapidno na klupi.

920
00:50:21,000 --> 00:50:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ujutro kreće s kaptola, s njepinčenim putem ide jeset.

921
00:50:25,000 --> 00:50:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na hodočaču Mariju Bislicu.

922
00:50:29,000 --> 00:50:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sretan, iza sebe imam 400 km.

923
00:50:33,000 --> 00:50:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Krešo dečko, znači svjedočim gospodinama od jebezini.

924
00:50:36,000 --> 00:50:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Molite gospodine, slobodi me svake oholosti, sve na svoju tvoju slavu.

925
00:50:40,000 --> 00:50:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači idem, taj dečko je Hrvać, obratio se.

926
00:50:45,000 --> 00:50:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mi fulamo tamo, kiša pada, fulamo pulut, završimo tamo nekim bregima, trči nazad.

927
00:50:51,000 --> 00:50:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trežak je taj put ono preko Slemona.

928
00:50:54,000 --> 00:50:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bi to mene, roko, otkut i snaga, ja trčim ispred njega.

929
00:50:59,000 --> 00:51:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jel, kakaj je onako sveto?

930
00:51:01,000 --> 00:51:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Snaga, duhom svetog, kako sam ako ja.

931
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] To nikad neću zavrati.

932
00:51:06,000 --> 00:51:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Opet smo se mi našli s tom skupinom.

933
00:51:08,000 --> 00:51:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sam se sužava put onako, ima uski put.

934
00:51:12,000 --> 00:51:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad jedna anegdota toga svega.

935
00:51:14,000 --> 00:51:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] I taj biskup mi i prati već.

936
00:51:16,000 --> 00:51:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Patrik, pot jednako odeđaš uvijek u mene sretim.

937
00:51:19,000 --> 00:51:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Više mu nije bilo jasno ništa.

938
00:51:21,000 --> 00:51:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I sad tako, sužava se, dolazim dva pol dva i čuo nekako priča.

939
00:51:26,000 --> 00:51:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je to bilo jatno i ja sam to cijeli život tražio.

940
00:51:29,000 --> 00:51:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije.

941
00:51:30,000 --> 00:51:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vidiš da je neko slobodan i on priča, nekako nije.

942
00:51:33,000 --> 00:51:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] A evo su ome, ono me, žaru.

943
00:51:36,000 --> 00:51:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja čekam da on dođe do mene ako starijim čovjek i ja.

944
00:51:39,000 --> 00:51:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] A vi ste župnik, mi je.

945
00:51:41,000 --> 00:51:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog vas boda sloju.

946
00:51:43,000 --> 00:51:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek se nosmije i odre napred.

947
00:51:45,000 --> 00:51:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sad dolazi do me ovaj drugi.

948
00:51:47,000 --> 00:51:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sada im njega i tako, oje župnike idio.

949
00:51:51,000 --> 00:51:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] I kaže ovo.

950
00:51:53,000 --> 00:51:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo pomočni biskup, ovaj je bio Gorski.

951
00:51:57,000 --> 00:51:59,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam Livan.

952
00:51:59,000 --> 00:52:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oje, Livan, koje je ugorski, koje je.

953
00:52:02,000 --> 00:52:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šaško mi je ostalo u glasju.

954
00:52:04,000 --> 00:52:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo interesantno.

955
00:52:05,000 --> 00:52:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, gospodin me je počeo ozdravljati.

956
00:52:18,000 --> 00:52:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tu dolazi ta ustrajnost.

957
00:52:21,000 --> 00:52:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je bila teška borba.

958
00:52:24,000 --> 00:52:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trebalo biti ustrajno.

959
00:52:26,000 --> 00:52:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sjećam se, Matija je bio sa vašim župnikom.

960
00:52:30,000 --> 00:52:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tada sam ih prvi put vidio u Šurkovcu.

961
00:52:33,000 --> 00:52:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin me stavio da budem poslužitelju Šurkovcu.

962
00:52:38,000 --> 00:52:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi koji su dolazili, koji me znaju

963
00:52:40,000 --> 00:52:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad su vidjeli da ja tamo slučtam one ljude,

964
00:52:42,000 --> 00:52:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] bake za ruku.

965
00:52:44,000 --> 00:52:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam znali šta.

966
00:52:45,000 --> 00:52:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da su i one vratili kad su vjetili.

967
00:52:48,000 --> 00:52:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nešto to mi je bilo dobro.

968
00:52:52,000 --> 00:52:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kodne mene mogu makati Šurkovcu.

969
00:52:56,000 --> 00:53:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] počinje ozdravljenje i psihičko, fizičko,

970
00:53:03,000 --> 00:53:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] počinje obraćenje.

971
00:53:05,000 --> 00:53:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, radikalno je krenulo tada.

972
00:53:07,000 --> 00:53:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] gospodin me ozdravljenje i osvobođao drogi.

973
00:53:09,000 --> 00:53:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Od...

974
00:53:11,000 --> 00:53:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] No od svega toga lošega,

975
00:53:14,000 --> 00:53:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam mislim da ne mogu nikad ozdraviti.

976
00:53:16,000 --> 00:53:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Počinje mi slati druge ljude.

977
00:53:19,000 --> 00:53:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Počinje mi slati ljude koji su živeli i koji žive u tim grijesima.

978
00:53:24,000 --> 00:53:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mafijaši, kamantarji.

979
00:53:27,000 --> 00:53:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Di šta, kako?

980
00:53:28,000 --> 00:53:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam samo vodit u Šurkovac.

981
00:53:30,000 --> 00:53:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja imam znači metom rođu ovako.

982
00:53:34,000 --> 00:53:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je ta moraš suze.

983
00:53:36,000 --> 00:53:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, svi mi tražimo Boga.

984
00:53:37,000 --> 00:53:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gledaš suze.

985
00:53:39,000 --> 00:53:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja da pomođa je mafijaš.

986
00:53:40,000 --> 00:53:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] On ovako polaža ruku.

987
00:53:44,000 --> 00:53:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Noće se dimut, dečka.

988
00:53:45,000 --> 00:53:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može se dimut.

989
00:53:46,000 --> 00:53:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako, brate.

990
00:53:48,000 --> 00:53:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek se obrata od dvoje djece.

991
00:53:49,000 --> 00:53:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Drugi, treći, peti.

992
00:53:51,000 --> 00:53:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog, hvala vam tome.

993
00:53:53,000 --> 00:53:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sećam se tamo je bila jedna žena koja je isto bila im reći tamo poslužiti.

994
00:53:59,000 --> 00:54:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je došla do mene kad sam počeo dolazi.

995
00:54:02,000 --> 00:54:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je došla do mene i kaže:

996
00:54:03,000 --> 00:54:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Kako se zoveš ti?"

997
00:54:04,000 --> 00:54:05,000
[UNKNOWN] Kažem brok.

998
00:54:05,000 --> 00:54:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Bog ti je puno dao."

999
00:54:06,000 --> 00:54:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Puno će i tražiti od tega."

1000
00:54:08,000 --> 00:54:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim dao što to znači.

1001
00:54:12,000 --> 00:54:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vraćam se sad.

1002
00:54:15,000 --> 00:54:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, došli sam u manjubisnicu.

1003
00:54:17,000 --> 00:54:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vratio sam pre ome zajednica.

1004
00:54:21,000 --> 00:54:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je krealo i moja duhovna okolost.

1005
00:54:23,000 --> 00:54:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sam se trenuo da je autobus, vodim međugorje sipo, biti počinio.

1006
00:54:30,000 --> 00:54:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mijem biti poznan.

1007
00:54:31,000 --> 00:54:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Opet moć, poznost, van, tamo.

1008
00:54:34,000 --> 00:54:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] I prije godinu nešto, ja čujem za to.

1009
00:54:42,000 --> 00:54:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oni krematija ispravija koju riješen, doživljavam drugo obraćenje.

1010
00:54:47,000 --> 00:54:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ako obraćenje traje svaki dal na mojom životu.

1011
00:54:50,000 --> 00:54:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] I dalje.

1012
00:54:51,000 --> 00:54:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde dolazi.

1013
00:54:52,000 --> 00:54:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna situacija gdje ja nisam znao da se vratim na crkveni sud.

1014
00:54:58,000 --> 00:55:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako me gospodin ozdravio.

1015
00:55:00,000 --> 00:55:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam u ovom momentu tada, gdje sam bio pod sakramentom biti ni svećenik, ni dimati cudu.

1016
00:55:05,000 --> 00:55:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] A gospodin me ozdravio je priprema za nešto.

1017
00:55:08,000 --> 00:55:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] A ja ne znam šta je.

1018
00:55:11,000 --> 00:55:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kao čovjek želio sam se nije skrasiti.

1019
00:55:13,000 --> 00:55:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je teško isto.

1020
00:55:15,000 --> 00:55:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sam vjerovom.

1021
00:55:17,000 --> 00:55:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ustrajao u tom sve svoje slabosti, grijehe padale.

1022
00:55:20,000 --> 00:55:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nastavio sam.

1023
00:55:21,000 --> 00:55:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Misa svaki dan.

1024
00:55:22,000 --> 00:55:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tada sretnem.

1025
00:55:23,000 --> 00:55:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] U Davoru Simonu.

1026
00:55:24,000 --> 00:55:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam je znao iz onog života.

1027
00:55:26,000 --> 00:55:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Padam.

1028
00:55:28,000 --> 00:55:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Boli svaki grijeh.

1029
00:55:30,000 --> 00:55:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mali, veliki boli.

1030
00:55:32,000 --> 00:55:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mista Domu.

1031
00:55:34,000 --> 00:55:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Poznajmo na meni.

1032
00:55:35,000 --> 00:55:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Roko.

1033
00:55:36,000 --> 00:55:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isus te voli.

1034
00:55:38,000 --> 00:55:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hrabu.

1035
00:55:40,000 --> 00:55:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Hrabu.

1036
00:55:41,000 --> 00:55:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moli za svoje neprijatelje.

1037
00:55:43,000 --> 00:55:45,000
[UNKNOWN] Ja gledamo nju ovako.

1038
00:55:45,000 --> 00:55:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne vjerujem da neko kojme se tako svi događava u životu.

1039
00:55:53,000 --> 00:55:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znamo njezni slučaj, manje više.

1040
00:55:55,000 --> 00:55:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moli za svoje neprijatelje.

1041
00:55:58,000 --> 00:56:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znali su me pitanje kako je tvoje svjedećanstvo?

1042
00:56:02,000 --> 00:56:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Moje.

1043
00:56:03,000 --> 00:56:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isto, ako si morano, samo što sam bio barava, ja sam se još i tukao.

1044
00:56:09,000 --> 00:56:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin zva svakoga od nas.

1045
00:56:11,000 --> 00:56:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer smo njegovi.

1046
00:56:13,000 --> 00:56:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] I on mi pošelje Simonu.

1047
00:56:15,000 --> 00:56:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da mi je pusu nekog rampa, ja mi reka dajde.

1048
00:56:17,000 --> 00:56:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Simone na njegove, idi.

1049
00:56:19,000 --> 00:56:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan je onaj.

1050
00:56:22,000 --> 00:56:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan dan sam se zgodala, svaki dan poruka, svaki dan uslava.

1051
00:56:26,000 --> 00:56:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nastavlja dalje moj život o tome.

1052
00:56:32,000 --> 00:56:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, nema ideje, ne mogu biti svećeni.

1053
00:56:35,000 --> 00:56:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mogu ni mancuru.

1054
00:56:37,000 --> 00:56:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki dan na misiji.

1055
00:56:39,000 --> 00:56:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam tamo u župi.

1056
00:56:40,000 --> 00:56:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Župik je Mario Migles.

1057
00:56:42,000 --> 00:56:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek mi isto nije znao.

1058
00:56:44,000 --> 00:56:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vidite čovjek svaki dan sam na misiji.

1059
00:56:46,000 --> 00:56:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, ne veličan grijeh.

1060
00:56:48,000 --> 00:56:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nego, iz čega me gospodin izvadio?

1061
00:56:53,000 --> 00:56:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Iz džavljeve utrobe me izvadio.

1062
00:56:56,000 --> 00:56:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije sam ja bio kređala, nije sam ja bio u njemu.

1063
00:56:58,000 --> 00:57:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] I župik Mario ima prijatelje neke iz Dubrava.

1064
00:57:03,000 --> 00:57:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sad imam priča kako se Roko Palić je ono bratio.

1065
00:57:07,000 --> 00:57:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koji? On ih ima puno.

1066
00:57:09,000 --> 00:57:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Koji? Ovo ono.

1067
00:57:10,000 --> 00:57:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I jedan je brat od ovog biskupa Palića.

1068
00:57:14,000 --> 00:57:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako će se reći.

1069
00:57:16,000 --> 00:57:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ovaj.

1070
00:57:18,000 --> 00:57:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže župik, pa evo ovaj.

1071
00:57:20,000 --> 00:57:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] Taj.

1072
00:57:22,000 --> 00:57:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nema šanse.

1073
00:57:24,000 --> 00:57:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Župik nije dao za mene.

1074
00:57:25,000 --> 00:57:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, svaki dan na misiji dolazi Božić, ja ostavim bez novaca.

1075
00:57:28,000 --> 00:57:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bez svega, da sam ostalo bez svega.

1076
00:57:30,000 --> 00:57:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin mi dopustio da ostavim bez svega.

1077
00:57:32,000 --> 00:57:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja završavam.

1078
00:57:33,000 --> 00:57:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Saravnica kod baki.

1079
00:57:34,000 --> 00:57:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ne ove tate, nego mamine.

1080
00:57:36,000 --> 00:57:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baka koja je vjerojila samo u tito.

1081
00:57:39,000 --> 00:57:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja završavam s bakom,

1082
00:57:46,000 --> 00:57:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] koje su u svjetskom ratu u baki ubili i oca i maj.

1083
00:57:52,000 --> 00:57:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] I bila je ta, pazi, da ovo to je jedno veliko svjetskom ratu i meni je jako drago za svako obraćenje.

1084
00:57:57,000 --> 00:58:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali, ovo je opet moja baka.

1085
00:58:01,000 --> 00:58:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, ja završavam to od bake.

1086
00:58:05,000 --> 00:58:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baki su ubili sve u drugom svjetskom ratu.

1087
00:58:08,000 --> 00:58:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nema nikoga.

1088
00:58:09,000 --> 00:58:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, mama je umrla, nema znači nikoga.

1089
00:58:14,000 --> 00:58:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja dolazim kod bake, tu su i dečki, dolazim tada i zajednice, to je pomagali mi.

1090
00:58:18,000 --> 00:58:24,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja dolazim kod bake, molim, klećim, zazivam duha svetoga.

1091
00:58:25,000 --> 00:58:26,000
[UNKNOWN] Ako govorilo, ovo nije normalno.

1092
00:58:26,000 --> 00:58:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prije si bio normalan. Prije sam nije bio normalan. Prije sam nije bio isto normalan.

1093
00:58:34,000 --> 00:58:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali sad mene ništa ne interesira neko molitva. Znači, to je bilo sve na glas.

1094
00:58:42,000 --> 00:58:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baka je bila kao djete na knježniku časnih sestara.

1095
00:58:47,000 --> 00:58:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer je bila bez roditelja.

1096
00:58:49,000 --> 00:58:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Uzeli se časni sese na knježnika koji je Tito pobjedio tad.

1097
00:58:52,000 --> 00:58:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Naravno, on je napravio to što je napravio, taj zločin.

1098
00:58:56,000 --> 00:58:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] I uzeli baku moju kao djete u te svoje mladinske akcije.

1099
00:58:59,000 --> 00:59:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] I oprali su joj mozak.

1100
00:59:01,000 --> 00:59:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] I njoj je drug Tito bio sve.

1101
00:59:04,000 --> 00:59:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve kada je umrla, ja sam nošao Tito u sliku.

1102
00:59:11,000 --> 00:59:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite sa Bogom.

1103
00:59:13,000 --> 00:59:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čuje se do čanstva Božje.

1104
00:59:15,000 --> 00:59:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja molim.

1105
00:59:17,000 --> 00:59:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jedno večer.

1106
00:59:19,000 --> 00:59:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baka ima onako mrenje.

1107
00:59:20,000 --> 00:59:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Starak, sam 24 godine.

1108
00:59:21,000 --> 00:59:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trini kada je bilo.

1109
00:59:23,000 --> 00:59:26,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ono počne moliti: "Oće naš."

1110
00:59:26,000 --> 00:59:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bako Bože, šta je ovo?

1111
00:59:28,000 --> 00:59:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog stavno čini čudo nekao ko mene.

1112
00:59:30,000 --> 00:59:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne mogu do sebe dođe, znam šta je.

1113
00:59:32,000 --> 00:59:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Miniju si mu načinio nešto novo.

1114
00:59:34,000 --> 00:59:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baka počne moliti: "Oće naš."

1115
00:59:40,000 --> 00:59:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga Anđele čuvaru.

1116
00:59:41,000 --> 00:59:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ne znam, jer dan danas Anđele čuvaru cijeli.

1117
00:59:43,000 --> 00:59:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se pitam, ja pitam Boga.

1118
00:59:47,000 --> 00:59:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve šta sam pitao gospodine, gospodine, nije dovoljno.

1119
00:59:49,000 --> 00:59:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao: "Bože, šta je ovo zbako, nema penzije, uvijek ona nešto žica."

1120
00:59:53,000 --> 00:59:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo si jedono isto.

1121
00:59:55,000 --> 00:59:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je to.

1122
00:59:58,000 --> 00:59:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sve šta sam borao.

1123
00:59:59,000 --> 01:00:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači tamo na krevetu i ja tu.

1124
01:00:00,000 --> 01:00:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ostalo upaljeno je svijetlo.

1125
01:00:01,000 --> 01:00:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Probudim se negdje uvijek u četiri.

1126
01:00:04,000 --> 01:00:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači u noći.

1127
01:00:06,000 --> 01:00:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači nisam ustajao.

1128
01:00:08,000 --> 01:00:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Samo sam otvorio oči.

1129
01:00:10,000 --> 01:00:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baka na leđima leži.

1130
01:00:14,000 --> 01:00:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Molio će naš Anđele čuvaru.

1131
01:00:15,000 --> 01:00:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga je poslije pala u krevet i pelene i tako dalje se to.

1132
01:00:23,000 --> 01:00:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mene je to bilo strašno i teško i drugačije.

1133
01:00:28,000 --> 01:00:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Međutim gospodine, kroz Šurkovac i kroz sve to dao mi milosti da ja to mogu.

1134
01:00:32,000 --> 01:00:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Mije joj baki pelene da jadam.

1135
01:00:34,000 --> 01:00:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja to niko je imao ljepo ja podigodni gospodine.

1136
01:00:37,000 --> 01:00:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na mene mi ja sad baki to.

1137
01:00:39,000 --> 01:00:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali gospodine čini čudan.

1138
01:00:41,000 --> 01:00:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Svako mi odna komu se preda.

1139
01:00:44,000 --> 01:00:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] I baka pada u pelene.

1140
01:00:46,000 --> 01:00:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači teške stvari se tu događaju s bakom.

1141
01:00:50,000 --> 01:00:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali prije toga, nego što je postala nepokretno.

1142
01:00:54,000 --> 01:00:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zapitam, baka kad se zadnji put ispovjerao?

1143
01:00:58,000 --> 01:01:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazi blagoslov kuća.

1144
01:01:01,000 --> 01:01:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Reću, bako ću blagosloviti stanju.

1145
01:01:03,000 --> 01:01:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je dobila rada u svijemenu.

1146
01:01:05,000 --> 01:01:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] I stanju je gdje se bilo narezanost.

1147
01:01:07,000 --> 01:01:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Na gordo mi daću ga samo tebi.

1148
01:01:09,000 --> 01:01:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kad umremu.

1149
01:01:10,000 --> 01:01:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ćeš mi da dati kad umreš?

1150
01:01:12,000 --> 01:01:16,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali baka je bila jaka.

1151
01:01:16,000 --> 01:01:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači život je negojio i tako.

1152
01:01:18,000 --> 01:01:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači 40 godina u tom stanu nikad nije bio sečan.

1153
01:01:21,000 --> 01:01:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači ona je bila komunista.

1154
01:01:23,000 --> 01:01:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije bila, ali je bila.

1155
01:01:27,000 --> 01:01:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ali kako sam i ja sad dišao s tim svim izmijeni.

1156
01:01:31,000 --> 01:01:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači to sam, ajmo reći malo to.

1157
01:01:33,000 --> 01:01:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Reć ću i lagano.

1158
01:01:35,000 --> 01:01:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako što bi dobili zajednice.

1159
01:01:37,000 --> 01:01:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer sam ja bio bez posla.

1160
01:01:38,000 --> 01:01:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bez ličega bili smo glavni.

1161
01:01:39,000 --> 01:01:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam tamo doživjavao kad každa s bakom.

1162
01:01:41,000 --> 01:01:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazi mi knjiga Svetog Augustina.

1163
01:01:42,000 --> 01:01:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ispovijesti.

1164
01:01:43,000 --> 01:01:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] Isto ne znam di sam.

1165
01:01:45,000 --> 01:01:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čitam ispovijesti.

1166
01:01:46,000 --> 01:01:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Preko ovo sam ja bio bio.

1167
01:01:47,000 --> 01:01:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo sam bio.

1168
01:01:48,000 --> 01:01:52,000
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin pozdravlja i obratio me preko svetog Augustina.

1169
01:01:52,000 --> 01:01:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže baka, jedan dan ti broko zove župnik.

1170
01:01:57,000 --> 01:01:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da, nosim hranu i ja kažem baki:

1171
01:01:59,000 --> 01:02:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Baka župnik je ovo da opozdravlja ta župnik.

1172
01:02:01,000 --> 01:02:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona, moj župnik, moj župnik.

1173
01:02:02,000 --> 01:02:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] I na kraju se jedan bako izmirio sa svećenicima.

1174
01:02:06,000 --> 01:02:08,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je bila zato s tim komunizmom.

1175
01:02:08,000 --> 01:02:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona, moj župnik, ma ništa ti ne valje.

1176
01:02:11,000 --> 01:02:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] Župnik je bolje od tebe ovo tamo.

1177
01:02:13,000 --> 01:02:14,000
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže ona meni:

1178
01:02:15,000 --> 01:02:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Zove župnika da boli svoju stanu.

1179
01:02:17,000 --> 01:02:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam znao di sam.

1180
01:02:18,000 --> 01:02:20,000
[SPEAKER_01] Trči njaka od župnika.

1181
01:02:20,000 --> 01:02:22,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znijeg je bio padov.

1182
01:02:22,000 --> 01:02:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] On kaže evo pišemo.

1183
01:02:25,000 --> 01:02:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mi je opisano uopće tamo.

1184
01:02:27,000 --> 01:02:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nije u župi.

1185
01:02:29,000 --> 01:02:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazim.

1186
01:02:30,000 --> 01:02:32,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazim ja doma.

1187
01:02:32,000 --> 01:02:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čekam s svećenika.

1188
01:02:33,000 --> 01:02:34,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čekam ja.

1189
01:02:34,000 --> 01:02:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čeka i ona.

1190
01:02:35,000 --> 01:02:36,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže u meni.

1191
01:02:36,000 --> 01:02:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odi sine.

1192
01:02:37,000 --> 01:02:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] Reci ponovo u župnik.

1193
01:02:39,000 --> 01:02:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da dođe gore.

1194
01:02:40,000 --> 01:02:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Neće one babe dole leć.

1195
01:02:41,000 --> 01:02:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nemoj te ići gore.

1196
01:02:42,000 --> 01:02:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kad vidim svećenici kažu:

1197
01:02:44,000 --> 01:02:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Jel ima još ko gore?"

1198
01:02:45,000 --> 01:02:46,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa rečeniči:

1199
01:02:46,000 --> 01:02:48,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Taj je baba ko mi sta, nemoj te tamo."

1200
01:02:48,000 --> 01:02:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] On je vjerovala u to.

1201
01:02:49,000 --> 01:02:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači i ona je vjerovala u to.

1202
01:02:51,000 --> 01:02:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je tu vjerovala.

1203
01:02:53,000 --> 01:02:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ponovno to čitam.

1204
01:02:56,000 --> 01:02:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] Župnik je tako i tako sretan.

1205
01:02:58,000 --> 01:03:00,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ima je bio neki zamenjik iz Mrkonića.

1206
01:03:00,000 --> 01:03:02,000
[SPEAKER_01] U stvari ko je pomagao tu.

1207
01:03:02,000 --> 01:03:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] Dolaze oni.

1208
01:03:03,000 --> 01:03:04,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ulaze iz križe.

1209
01:03:04,000 --> 01:03:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Baka, od načine muša svećenika."

1210
01:03:06,000 --> 01:03:08,000
[SPEAKER_00] "Oče naš ko je jesu."

1211
01:03:08,000 --> 01:03:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] Olajko, poljubite baka, krije.

1212
01:03:12,000 --> 01:03:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Olajko, krije.

1213
01:03:14,000 --> 01:03:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Olajko, krije.

1214
01:03:16,000 --> 01:03:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] Olajko, krije.

1215
01:03:18,000 --> 01:03:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] I eto, blagoslovinica.

1216
01:03:19,000 --> 01:03:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da skratim, toliko toga ima.

1217
01:03:21,000 --> 01:03:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da skratim i ovaj...

1218
01:03:23,000 --> 01:03:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Blagoslovinu.

1219
01:03:25,000 --> 01:03:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Skriješ, kažem mi:

1220
01:03:27,000 --> 01:03:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Alo neksurdije ste tu."

1221
01:03:29,000 --> 01:03:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] Sretani, bileni svećeni.

1222
01:03:33,000 --> 01:03:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] I ovaj...

1223
01:03:35,000 --> 01:03:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] To prođe i krije mi:

1224
01:03:37,000 --> 01:03:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Baka, ispovjedalo se."

1225
01:03:41,000 --> 01:03:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Olajko, ne svi."

1226
01:03:45,000 --> 01:03:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] Takva radost.

1227
01:03:47,000 --> 01:03:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja trčim.

1228
01:03:49,000 --> 01:03:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bog čini čudesa.

1229
01:03:51,000 --> 01:03:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] Da ja ne mogu primiti.

1230
01:03:53,000 --> 01:03:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] Čovjek ja to ne mogu primiti.

1231
01:03:55,000 --> 01:03:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja trčim.

1232
01:03:57,000 --> 01:03:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kod kapelana, ko baka se hoće ispovjedati.

1233
01:03:59,000 --> 01:04:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] On kaže: "Dolazim."

1234
01:04:01,000 --> 01:04:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pitam ja baku, prijateljka ko baka,

1235
01:04:05,000 --> 01:04:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] čekajućih kapelana.

1236
01:04:07,000 --> 01:04:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam molio, iz bilo sloci.

1237
01:04:09,000 --> 01:04:10,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam molio u Kukinu.

1238
01:04:10,000 --> 01:04:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja se pitao baku:

1239
01:04:11,000 --> 01:04:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] "Baka, kaj se za njim put ispovjedalo?"

1240
01:04:13,000 --> 01:04:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] 1947. godine.

1241
01:04:17,000 --> 01:04:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] Prije 69. godine.

1242
01:04:19,000 --> 01:04:21,000
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam kako se hoće.

1243
01:04:21,000 --> 01:04:23,000
[SPEAKER_01] Umrla je u Božjoj milosti, ispovjedalo se.

1244
01:04:23,000 --> 01:04:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kapelani držao to,

1245
01:04:25,000 --> 01:04:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] tamo sprovno,

1246
01:04:27,000 --> 01:04:29,000
[SPEAKER_01] misljenje šta to kaže.

1247
01:04:29,000 --> 01:04:31,000
[SPEAKER_01] Spasilo se, ja sam bio,

1248
01:04:31,000 --> 01:04:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] toliko sam je bolio, ja sam bio sretan.

1249
01:04:33,000 --> 01:04:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] Spasilo se.

1250
01:04:35,000 --> 01:04:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon 69. godine.

1251
01:04:37,000 --> 01:04:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga,

1252
01:04:41,000 --> 01:04:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] vraćam se sada na ovo,

1253
01:04:45,000 --> 01:04:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] na crkveni sud.

1254
01:04:47,000 --> 01:04:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ta bivša cura,

1255
01:04:51,000 --> 01:04:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] jer mi nije bila žena,

1256
01:04:53,000 --> 01:04:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] je bila,

1257
01:04:56,000 --> 01:04:59,000
[SPEAKER_01] predala tu tužbu.

1258
01:04:59,000 --> 01:05:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, prije nego što sam se ja i obratio,

1259
01:05:01,000 --> 01:05:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] predala je tu tužbu na ovo crkvi.

1260
01:05:03,000 --> 01:05:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] srkvi.

1261
01:05:05,000 --> 01:05:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to...

1262
01:05:13,000 --> 01:05:15,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šurkovać sad, ja?

1263
01:05:15,000 --> 01:05:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] I to...

1264
01:05:25,000 --> 01:05:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1265
01:05:27,000 --> 01:05:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] u tom periodu dolazim na crkveni sud,

1266
01:05:33,000 --> 01:05:35,000
[SPEAKER_01] ona je predala tu tužbu,

1267
01:05:35,000 --> 01:05:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] je li dolazim na crkveni sud,

1268
01:05:37,000 --> 01:05:39,000
[SPEAKER_01] kaže sve šta sam bio oko Ivana sada.

1269
01:05:39,000 --> 01:05:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odlazim,

1270
01:05:41,000 --> 01:05:43,000
[SPEAKER_01] i nakon godine dana mi šalje sestra,

1271
01:05:43,000 --> 01:05:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] slikao da je došao nešto na ovdje od biskupije.

1272
01:05:45,000 --> 01:05:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] Slikava je taj dokument, ja vidim potreba o ništanosti braka.

1273
01:05:51,000 --> 01:05:53,000
[SPEAKER_01] To će sam kod Davide.

1274
01:05:53,000 --> 01:05:55,000
[SPEAKER_01] To će sam kod Davide od žubnika,

1275
01:05:55,000 --> 01:05:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] sve je slobna čovjeka.

1276
01:05:57,000 --> 01:06:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] To će bio sam slobna.

1277
01:06:03,000 --> 01:06:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga...

1278
01:06:05,000 --> 01:06:07,000
[SPEAKER_01] dolazim od sve svete,

1279
01:06:07,000 --> 01:06:09,000
[SPEAKER_01] dolazim kod prijatelja jednog,

1280
01:06:09,000 --> 01:06:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] koji me zna iz danog života, ima teretarno, tamo,

1281
01:06:11,000 --> 01:06:13,000
[SPEAKER_01] i to dolazim.

1282
01:06:13,000 --> 01:06:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je isto u tom 7.7-u, sam nije bio agresivno kao ja.

1283
01:06:15,000 --> 01:06:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dolazim on sad u snužnjem.

1284
